---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">About Us</h1>

    <!-- Welcome Section -->
    <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600">
        Welcome to HoustonFuneralGuide.com, where compassion meets guidance, and the community of Houston finds clarity in times of loss. Nestled in the heart of Houston, TX, our platform stands as a beacon of support and knowledge, dedicated to guiding residents through one of life's most challenging journeys â€“ saying farewell to loved ones.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          At HoustonFuneralGuide.com, our mission is more than just providing information; it's about creating a compassionate, understanding, and informative sanctuary for those grappling with loss. We understand that dealing with funeral arrangements can be overwhelming, especially during times of grief. That's why we are committed to offering a guiding hand through this journey, ensuring you can honor your loved ones with the dignity and respect they deserve.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why HoustonFuneralGuide.com?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Local Expertise</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Being based in Houston, we bring a wealth of local knowledge and resources. We understand the unique needs and preferences of our community, making us well-equipped to offer relevant and practical advice.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Comprehensive Resources</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            From understanding funeral service options to navigating legal requirements and cultural customs in Houston, our platform covers all facets of funeral planning and bereavement support.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Questions & Answers Hub</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our interactive Q&A section allows Houston residents to seek answers to specific questions about funeral services. This platform fosters a community where shared experiences and knowledge make a difficult time a bit easier to navigate.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Educational Articles</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our regularly updated blog features articles on various topics, including how to choose the right funeral service, ways to celebrate the life of your loved one, and advice on coping with grief.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Personalized Assistance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Recognizing that each family's needs are unique, we offer personalized guidance. Our team is always ready to assist you in finding the right services, products, and support tailored to your specific situation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Community Connection</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We believe in the power of community during trying times. HoustonFuneralGuide.com not only provides information but also connects you with local support groups, counselors, and other resources within Houston.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Commitment Section -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Commitment to Houston</h2>
      <div class="bg-primary text-white p-8 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Houston is more than just a location for us; it's our home, filled with diverse communities and stories. At HoustonFuneralGuide.com, we are committed to being a part of your story, offering a comforting hand during the toughest of chapters.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Our dedication to serving Houston's residents is unwavering, as we continue to evolve and adapt to meet your needs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Need Assistance?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">Our team is here to help you through this difficult time.</p>
      <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-bold hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors inline-block">
        Call Us: (123) 456-7890
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>